-- Dominique Strauss-Kahn, Anne Sinclair Separated, Magazine Says
-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 2012-06-29T00:45:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/dominique-strauss-kahn-anne-sinclair-separated-magazine-says.html
Dominique Strauss-Kahn , the former
head of the International Monetary Fund, and Anne Sinclair, who
would have marked 21 years of marriage on Nov. 26, have
separated, French magazine Closer reported on its website.  The couple have been living apart for almost a month, the
magazine said.  Story link:  http://tinyurl.com/7rzhqbk   To contact the reporter on this story:
